@startuml US01_Browse_Posts_Guest
title US-01: Browse Posts (Guest User)

|Guest User|
start
:(1) Open forum website;

|System|
:(2) Load landing page UI;
:(3) Request public posts;

:(4) Fetch posts from database;
if (Posts available?) then (Yes)
  :(5) Return post list;
else (No)
  :(5) Return empty result;
endif

|Guest User|
:(6) View post list / empty state;

if (Select a post?) then (Yes)
  |System|
  :(7) Fetch post details;
  :(8) Fetch comments;

  |Guest User|
  :(9) View post content and comments;
else (No)
endif

stop
@enduml